#: ../../source/advance.rst:3
msgid "Advanced Usage"
msgstr "高级用法"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:6
msgid "MPS Simulator"
msgstr "MPS 模拟器"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:8
msgid ""
"TensorCircuit-NG provides Matrix Product State (MPS) simulation as an "
"efficient alternative to exact simulation for quantum circuits. MPS "
"simulation can handle larger quantum systems by trading off accuracy for "
"computational efficiency."
msgstr "TensorCircuit-NG 提供了矩阵乘积态 (MPS) 模拟，作为量子线路精确模拟的高效替代方案。MPS 模拟可以通过权衡精度与计算效率来处理更大规模的量子系统。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:10
msgid ""
"MPS simulator is very straightforward to use, we provide the same set of "
"API for ``MPSCircuit`` as ``Circuit``, the only new line is to set the "
"bond dimension for the new simulator."
msgstr "MPS 模拟器的使用非常直观。我们为 ``MPSCircuit`` 提供了与 ``Circuit`` 相同的一套 API，唯一的区别是需要为新的模拟器设置截断维度 (bond dimension)。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:18
msgid ""
"The larger bond dimension we set, the better approximation ratio (of "
"course the more computational cost we pay)."
msgstr "设置的截断维度越大，近似比例就越好（当然，计算成本也会相应增加）。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:22
msgid "Stacked gates syntax"
msgstr "堆叠门语法"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:24
msgid ""
"Stacked-gate is a simple syntactic sugar rendering circuit construction "
"easily when multiple gate of the same type are applied on different "
"qubits, namely, the index for gate call can accept list of ints instead "
"of one integer."
msgstr "堆叠门 (Stacked-gate) 是一种简单的语法糖，当需要在不同量子比特上应用多个同类型量子门时，它可以简化线路构建。即量子门调用的索引可以接受整数列表，而不仅仅是一个整数。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:71
msgid "Split Two-qubit Gates"
msgstr "分解双量子比特门"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:73
msgid ""
"The two-qubit gates applied on the circuit can be decomposed via SVD, "
"which may further improve the optimality of the contraction pathfinding."
msgstr "应用在电路上的双量子比特门可以通过 SVD 进行分解，这可以进一步提高收缩路径查找的最优性。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:75
msgid "``split`` configuration can be set at circuit-level or gate-level."
msgstr "``split`` 配置可以在电路级或门级设置。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:96
msgid ""
"Note ``max_singular_values`` must be specified to make the whole "
"procedure static and thus jittable."
msgstr "请注意 ``max_singular_values`` 必须被指定以使整个过程成为静态的，从而支持 JIT 编译。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:99
msgid "Analog circuit simulation"
msgstr "模拟电路模拟"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:101
msgid ""
"TensorCircuit-NG support digital-analog hybrid simulation (say cases in "
"Rydberg atom arrays), where the analog part is simulated by the neural "
"differential equation solver given the API to specify a time dependent "
"Hamiltonian. The simulation is still differentiable and jittable. Only "
"jax backend is supported for analog simulation as the neural ode engine "
"is built on top of jax."
msgstr "TensorCircuit-NG 支持数模混合模拟（例如里德堡原子阵列中的情况），其中模拟部分由神经常微分方程 (ODE) 求解器模拟，并提供指定随时间变化的哈密顿量的 API。模拟过程仍然是可微且可 JIT 编译的。由于神经网络 ODE 引擎是构建在 JAX 之上的，因此模拟模拟目前仅支持 JAX 后端。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:104
msgid ""
"This utility is super helpful for optimizing quantum control or "
"investigating digital-analog hybrid variational quantum schemes."
msgstr "该工具对于优化量子控制或研究数模混合变分量子方案非常有用。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:106
msgid ""
"We support two modes of analog simulation, where "
":py:meth:`tensorcircuit.experimental.evol_global` evolve the state via a "
"Hamiltonian define on the whole system, and "
":py:meth:`tensorcircuit.experimental.evol_local` evolve the state via a "
"Hamiltonian define on a local subsystem."
msgstr "我们支持两种模拟模拟模式：:py:meth:`tensorcircuit.experimental.evol_global` 通过定义在整个系统上的哈密顿量演化状态，而 :py:meth:`tensorcircuit.experimental.evol_local` 通过定义在局部子系统上的哈密顿量演化状态。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:110
msgid ""
"``evol_global`` uses sparse Hamiltonian while ``evol_local`` uses dense "
"Hamiltonian."
msgstr "``evol_global`` 使用稀疏哈密顿量，而 ``evol_local`` 使用稠密哈密顿量。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:153
msgid "Time Evolution"
msgstr "时间演化"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:155
msgid ""
"TensorCircuit-NG provides several methods for simulating quantum time "
"evolution, including exact diagonalization, Krylov subspace methods, and "
"ODE-based approaches. These methods are essential for studying quantum "
"dynamics, particularly in many-body systems, and all support automatic "
"differentiation (AD) and JIT compilation for enhanced performance."
msgstr "TensorCircuit-NG 提供了多种模拟量子时间演化的方法，包括精确对角化、Krylov 子空间方法和基于 ODE 的方法。这些方法对于研究量子动力学（特别是多体系统）至关重要，并且都支持自动微分 (AD) 和 JIT 编译以提高性能。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:158
msgid "**Exact Diagonalization:**"
msgstr "**精确对角化 (ED):**"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:160
msgid ""
"For small systems where full diagonalization is feasible, the "
":py:meth:`tensorcircuit.timeevol.ed_evol` method provides exact time "
"evolution by directly computing matrix exponentials (alias "
":py:meth:`tensorcircuit.timeevol.hamiltonian_evol`):"
msgstr "对于全对角化可行的小系统，:py:meth:`tensorcircuit.timeevol.ed_evol` 方法通过直接计算矩阵指数提供精确的时间演化（别名 :py:meth:`tensorcircuit.timeevol.hamiltonian_evol`）："

#: ../../source/advance.rst:196
msgid ""
"This method is particularly efficient for time-independent Hamiltonians "
"as it uses eigendecomposition to compute the evolution. It provides exact"
" results but is limited to small systems (typically <16 qubits) due to "
"the exponential growth of the Hilbert space."
msgstr "该方法对于与时间无关的哈密顿量特别有效，因为它使用特征值分解来计算演化。它提供精确的结果，但由于希尔伯特空间的指数增长，仅限于小系统（通常 <16 个量子比特）。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:201
msgid ""
"For real time evolution, the time should be chosen as ``times = 1.j * "
"tc.backend.convert_to_tensor([0.0, 0.5, 1.0, 2.0])``"
msgstr "对于实时演化，时间应选择为 ``times = 1.j * tc.backend.convert_to_tensor([0.0, 0.5, 1.0, 2.0])``"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:204
msgid "**Krylov Subspace Methods:**"
msgstr "**Krylov 子空间方法:**"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:206
msgid ""
"For larger systems where exact diagonalization becomes intractable, the "
"Krylov subspace method provides an efficient approximation. The "
":py:meth:`tensorcircuit.timeevol.krylov_evol` function implements this "
"approach:"
msgstr "对于精确对角化难以处理的大系统，Krylov 子空间方法提供了一种高效的近似。:py:meth:`tensorcircuit.timeevol.krylov_evol` 函数实现了这种方法："

#: ../../source/advance.rst:243
msgid ""
"The Krylov method constructs a small subspace that captures the essential"
" dynamics, making it possible to simulate larger systems efficiently. It "
"supports both standard and scan-based jit-friendly implementations:"
msgstr "Krylov 方法构建了一个捕捉本质动力学的小子空间，从而能够高效地模拟大型系统。它支持标准实现和基于 scan 的 JIT 友好实现："

#: ../../source/advance.rst:254
msgid "**ODE-Based Evolution:**"
msgstr "**基于 ODE 的演化:**"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:256
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"For time-dependent Hamiltonians or when fine control over the evolution "
"process is needed, TensorCircuit provides ODE-based evolution methods. "
"These methods solve the time-dependent Schrödinger equation directly by "
"integrating the equation :math:`i\\frac{d}{dt}|\\psi(t)\\rangle = "
"H(t)|\\psi(t)\\rangle`."
msgstr "对于随时间变化的哈密顿量，或者需要对演化过程进行精细控制时，TensorCircuit 提供了基于 ODE 的演化方法。这些方法通过积分方程 :math:`i\\frac{d}{dt}|\\psi(t)\\rangle = H(t)|\\psi(t)\\rangle` 直接求解随时间变化的薛定谔方程。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:259
msgid ""
"TensorCircuit provides two ODE-based evolution methods depending on "
"whether the Hamiltonian acts on the entire system or just a local "
"subsystem:"
msgstr "根据哈密顿量是作用于整个系统还是仅作用于局部子系统，TensorCircuit 提供了两种基于 ODE 的演化方法："

#: ../../source/advance.rst:261
msgid ""
"**Global Evolution** (:py:meth:`tensorcircuit.timeevol.ode_evol_global`):"
" For time-dependent Hamiltonians acting on the entire system. The "
"Hamiltonian should be provided in sparse matrix format for efficiency."
msgstr "**全局演化** (:py:meth:`tensorcircuit.timeevol.ode_evol_global`)：适用于作用于整个系统的随时间变化的哈密顿量。为了效率，哈密顿量应以稀疏矩阵格式提供。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:344
msgid ""
"**Local Evolution** (:py:meth:`tensorcircuit.timeevol.ode_evol_local`): "
"For time-dependent Hamiltonians acting on a subsystem of qubits. The "
"Hamiltonian should be provided in dense matrix format."
msgstr "**局部演化** (:py:meth:`tensorcircuit.timeevol.ode_evol_local`)：适用于作用于量子比特子系统的随时间变化的哈密顿量。哈密顿量应以稠密矩阵格式提供。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:389
msgid ""
"Both ODE-based methods support automatic differentiation and JIT "
"compilation when using the JAX backend, making them suitable for "
"optimization tasks in quantum control and variational quantum algorithms."
" The methods integrate the time-dependent Schrödinger equation using "
"JAX's ODE solvers, providing flexible and efficient simulation of quantum"
" dynamics with time-dependent Hamiltonians."
msgstr "两种基于 ODE 的方法在绘制 JAX 后端时都支持自动微分和 JIT 编译，使其适用于量子控制和变分量子算法中的优化任务。这些方法使用 JAX 的 ODE 求解器积分随时间变化的薛定谔方程，为具有随时间变化的哈密顿量的量子动力学提供灵活且高效的模拟。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:394
msgid ""
"ODE-based methods currently only support the JAX backend due to the "
"dependency on JAX's ODE solvers."
msgstr "由于依赖 JAX 的 ODE 求解器，基于 ODE 的方法目前仅支持 JAX 后端。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:395
msgid ""
"Global evolution requires sparse Hamiltonian matrices for efficiency with"
" large systems."
msgstr "全局演化在大系统中需要稀疏哈密顿矩阵以保证效率。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:396
msgid ""
"Local evolution requires dense Hamiltonian matrices and is suitable for "
"subsystems with few qubits."
msgstr "局部演化需要稠密哈密顿矩阵，适用于量子比特数较少的子系统。"

#: ../../source/advance.rst:397
msgid ""
"Both methods support callback functions to compute observables during "
"evolution without storing all state vectors."
msgstr "两种方法都支持回调函数，以便在演化过程中计算可观测核，而无需存储所有状态向量。"

