#: ../../source/advance.rst:581
msgid "Working with MPO format:"
msgstr "使用 MPO 格式："

#: ../../source/advance.rst:583
msgid ""
"TensorCircuit-NG supports conversion from different MPO (Matrix Product "
"Operator) formats, particularly from TensorNetwork and Quimb libraries. "
"This is useful when you want to leverage existing MPO implementations or "
"convert between different frameworks."
